1990;;Till There Was You;;Australian;;John Seale;;Mark Harmon, Deborah Unger, Jeroen Krabbe, Shane Briant, Lech Mackiewicz;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Till_There_Was_You_(1990_film);;Frank Flynn is summonsed from New York City to Vanuatu by his brother Charlie . He arrives only to find Charlie dead, and becomes involved with his late brother's partner, Viv, and Viv's unhappy wife, Anna.